highlights.text: “Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 230 weeks straight.
Doja Cat has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Kiss Me More (feat. SZA)” is the highest at #6.
“Bad Habits” by Ed Sheeran is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #7.
“Poblado - Remix” by J Balvin, KAROL G, Nicky Jam, Crissin, Totoy El Frio, and Natan & Shander is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 64 spots at #37.
